docs {
  `GET health.php` and `GET ready.php` (ARCHITECTURE.md §3.4). Real
  files: `public/health.php`, `public/ready.php`. Both are deliberately
  UNAUTHENTICATED (no login/CSRF needed) -- an uptime prober cannot hold
  an EMR session. Can be run before or independent of every other folder.
